# System Actions (`touch-system-actions`)

## When to Use
- Run power, lock, audio, brightness, and window actions.

## Trigger
- Feature ID: `system.actions`
- Commands: `system / sys / 系统 / 系统操作`

## Core Capabilities
- 系统操作中心：电源、锁屏、音量、亮度、主窗口
- Supported platforms: `win32, darwin`

## Config & Data
- Config/data files: None (no manual config file needed for MVP)
- Plugin directory: `plugins/touch-system-actions`

## Permissions
- Required: `system.shell`

## Quick Start
1. In CoreBox, type `system`.
2. Press Enter on the action you need.
3. Grant permissions when prompted.
